<div class="hero hero-sm">
  <div>
    <h1>{{page.title}}</h1>
    <p>Edit the wording of the platform's outbound emails. Each template is one distinct message; personal values are filled in at send time through its merge fields. Editing only: new templates arrive with code changes.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">
  <p class="text-muted">{{content.totalCount}} templates{{#if content.hasDisabled}} &middot; {{content.disabledCount}} disabled{{/if}}</p>

  {{#each content.rows}}
    <div class="card mb-2">
      <div class="card-title"><a href="{{editHref}}">{{templateKey}}</a>{{#if isDisabled}} <span class="badge">disabled</span>{{/if}}</div>
      <p class="card-meta">{{subjectTemplate}}</p>
      <p class="card-meta fs-sm text-muted">classification: {{classification}} &middot; updated {{updatedAtDisplay}}</p>
    </div>
  {{/each}}
</div>
